Okay, so I believe the names in (()) are the ruins, and obviously the Tower and Keep, are their respective objectives. What I am unclear on are what things like “Lumber Mill” and “Fishing Village” are in the API call for https://api.guildwars2.com/v1/wvw/objective_names.json

It seems the Wiki is unclear on this portion, and the search feature for the forums returns “0 Results” no matter what I type in. Would someone mind explaining the various names in detail?
